1558235.title: 227 West 45th Street (Seventh Avenue - Eighth Avenue)
1558235.folder: 227 West 45th Street (Seventh Avenue - Eighth Avenue), Manhattan, NY

713234f-a.text:
West 45th Street, south side, west from Eighth to Ninth Aves., showing the Martin Beck Theater (No. 302) adjoining the 3-story structure at the S.W. corner of Eighth Ave. This set consists of a negative and a positive view.

November 1935.

W.P.A. Photo.
